---
title: Roast Cauliflower Burrito Rice Bowl with Corn Salsa & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Try this twist on a burrito bowl, with spiced and roasted cauliflower, plus classic Mexican sides topping a generous
serve of our aromatic garlic rice. It's the ideal recipe to try something new and taste just how versatile veggies can be!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
